      <varlistentry>
        <term><option>-c</option></term>
        <term><option>--config-dir</option></term>
        <listitem>
          <para>Use an alternate location (which will be created if it does not exist) for the configuration directory.</para>
          <para>This is useful for using/trying specific configuration values for a particular session without changing ones normal settings.</para>
        </listitem>
